    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example of the S54-powered legend. The 3.2L inline-six maintains factory-spec compression across all cylinders, with the double-VANOS system recently overhauled for optimal cam timing. The chassis is structurally flawless, featuring proactive subframe reinforcement and fresh bushings for sharpened turn-in. Power is delivered through a crisp 6-speed manual to a variable M-differential. Finished in Carbon Black over Nappa leather, the paint depth and interior integrity are consistent with a climate-controlled collector piece. No mechanical or electronic faults; this",
