    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Presenting a true collector-grade masterpiece that defines the term 'mint.' This vehicle has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment, resulting in an exterior finish that is entirely free of rock chips, swirl marks, or imperfections. The factory paint retains its deep, original luster, complemented by a professional ceramic coating applied just last season. Inside, the cabin is a time capsule; the premium leather upholstery remains supple with no bolster wear, the carpets are spotless, and the 'new car' scent persists. Every electronic feature, from the high-fidelity sound system to the dual-zone climate control, operates with factory precision. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach. It comes with a binder of exhaustive service records documenting every fluid change and inspection performed by certified technicians. The engine bay is immaculate, the undercarriage is rust-free, and the transmission shifts with seamless fluidity. This sale includes the original window sticker, all three factory keys, and the complete set of owner's manuals. For the buyer who demands perfection and transparency, this vehicle stands as a flawless example of its model.",
